events.body:
Concept ACK

Add `addrinfo` to the list of options
https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/65f30e4c21e94b775853392b7e0de5c7fd3de488/doc/tor.md#L13
``` diff
  - in the output of the CLI `-netinfo` peer connections dashboard
+ - in the output of the CLI `-addrinfo` command
```

Then your paragraph is an explanation of this option much like lines 15&16 are for the debug log option.

> Concept ACK
> 
> Add `addrinfo` to the list of options

Thanks for having a look! That list is of ways to see your local onion address, so it seems to me that this is a different topic and use context and doesn't belong in that list.

ACK 65f30e4c21e94b775853392b7e0de5c7fd3de488


> That list is of ways to see your local onion address, so it seems to me that this is a different topic and use context and doesn't belong in that list.

Right, whoops! 🥃
